    "en": {
      "title": "Wimalaweera's story about Ranjan",
      "author": "unknown",
      "body_lines": [
        "Mr. Wimalaweera Dissanayake said that he is heartily happy that Mr. Ranjan Ramanayake is not a criminal and he is released.",
        "Former Minister Ranjan Ramanayake said that he is not a thief or a corrupt person and said that he is a beautiful person.",
        "Mr. Wimalaweera Dissanayake added that he wished him well."
      ],
